		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Memblers has a good point. Maybe the game is using different character sets for the top and bottom parts of the screen, and you placed the text in an area where it's still using top characters. You must make the switch happen earlier.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


