		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Not only that, but it seems the color used for the tiles is wrong too (brown instead of white), since you moved the text into another attribute block.
<br />So you'd have to hack the MMC3's scanline interrupt to happen sooner, hack what is written to the attribute (color) table OR deal with the text being lower.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


